hadiths[42]{hadithnumber,text}:
488,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sab sey behtar din jis mein suraj nikla, Juma ka din hai, isi din Adam ko paida kya gaya, isi din unhen jannat mein dakhil kya gaya, isi din unhen jannat sey nikala gaya, aur qiyamat bhi isi din qaaim hogi '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Lubaba, Salman , Abu-Zar , Saad bin Ubada aur Aus bin Aus (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
489,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Juma key roz us ghadi ko jismein dua ki qubuliyat ki ummid ki jati hai Asr sey ley kar suraj doobney tak key darmiyan talash karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- ye hadees Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi kaee sanadon sey marvi hai, 3- Muhammad bin abi Humed zaeef maaney jatey hain, baaz ehle-ilm ney unkey hifz key talluq sey un ki tazeef ki hai, unhen Hammad bin abi Humed bhi kaha jata hai, neez kaha jata hai ke yehi abu Ibrahim Ansari hain aur ye munkire-hadees hain, 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke ye ghadi jis mein qubuliyate-dua ki ummid ki jati hai Asr key baad sey suraj doobney key darmiyan hai, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain. Ahmed kehtey hain : is ghadi key silsiley mein jis mein dua ki qubuliyat ki ummid ki jati hai ziyada tar hadisein yehi aai hain ke ye Asr key baad sey suraj doobney key darmiyan hai, neez suraj dhalney key baad bhi uskey honey ki ummid ki jati hai."
490,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Juma main eik ghadi aisi hai ke banda jo kuch bhi is mein maangta hai Allah usey ata karta hai'' , logon ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! ye kon si ghadi hai? aap ney farmaya : '' namaz ( Juma ( khadi honey key waqt sey ley kar us sey palatney yani namaz khatam honey tak hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Amr bin Auf ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Musa , Abu-Zar , Salman , Abdullah bin Salam , abu-Lubaba, Saad bin Ubada aur abu-Umama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
491,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey behtar din jis mein suraj nikla Jume ka din hai. isi din Adam paida kiye gaey, isi din wo jannat mein dakhil kiye gaey, isi din wo jannat sey (zameen par utarey gaey) is din main eik ghadi aisi hai ke jisey Muslim banda namaz ki haalat mein paey aur Allah sey is mein kuchh talab karey to Allah usey zarur ata farmaeyga. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : phir main Abdullah bin Salam sey mila aur un sey is hadees ka zikr kiya to unhoney kaha : main ye ghadi achchhi tarah janta hun, mainey kaha : mujhey bhi uskey barey mein bataiye aur is silsiley mein mujh sey bukhl (kanjoosi) na keejiye, unhoney kaha : ye Asr key baad sey ley kar suraj doobney ke darmiyan hai, is par mainey kaha : ye Asr ke baad kaisey ho sakti hai jabke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : ''usey musalman banda haalate namaz mein paey aur ye waqt aisa hai jis mein namaz nahin padhi jati? to Abdullah bin Salam ney kaha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye nahin farmaya hai ke jo shakhs namaz key intizar mein kisi jagah betha rahey to wo bhi namaz hi mein hota hai? mainey kaha : kyon nahin, zarur farmaya hai to unhoney kaha : to yehi murad hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees main eik taweel (lamba) qissa hai. 2- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 3- aur aap ke is qol (أخبرني بها wala تضنن بها علي) key maana hain ""isey mujhey bataaney mein bukhl na keejiye.""  «ضنّ» key maana bukhl (kanjoosi) ke hain aur «ظنين» key maana , muttahim (jis par jhoot wagaira ka ilzaam laga ho) key hain."
492,"unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' jo Juma ki namaz key liye aaye usey chahiye ke) pehley ( ghusl kar ley '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is baat mein umr , abu Saeed Khudri , Jabir , Bara , Aaisha aur Abu-Darda sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
493,"neez ibn Shahab Zohri sey ye hadees b-tareeq : الزهري an عبد الله بن عبد الله بن عمر an أبيه an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم bhi marvi hai, Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Zohri ki hadees jisey unhoney b-tareeq : « Salim an Abeeh Abdullah bin umr »riwayat ki hai aur jo hadees unhoney b-tareeq : « Abdullah bin Abdullah bin umr an Abeeh Abdullah bin umr » riwayat ki hai dono hadisein sahih hain, aur Zohri key baaz talaamiza ney isey b-tareeq : «Zohri an aal abdullah bin umr an abdullah bin umr » riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Juma key din key ghusl key silsiley mein b-tareeq : « ibne-Umar an umr an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » marfooan marvi hai, ( jo aagey aa rahi hai) aur ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
494,"umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Juma key roz khutba dey rahey they ke usi doran Sahaba mein sey eik shakhs padhi. ( masjid mein) dakhil huye, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney puchha : ye kon sa waqt ( aaney ka ( hai? to unhoney kaha : mainey sirf itni der ki ke Azan suni aur bas wuzu kar key aa gaya hun, is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : tum ney sirf ( wuzu hi par iktifa kya ( halanke tumhen malum hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ghusl ka hukm diya hai?"
495,"Zohri sey yehi hadees marvi hai. aur Malik ney bhi ye hadees b-tareeq : « an Zohri an Salim  riwayat ki hai, wo Salim bin umr kehtey hain ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Juma key din khutba dey rahey they, aagey unhoney puri hadees zikr ki . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mainey is silsiley mein Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey puchha to unhoney kaha : sahih Zohri ki hadees hai jisey unhoney b-tareeq : « Salim an Abiy » riwayat ki hai. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke Malik sey bhi usi hadees ki tarah marvi hai, unhoney b-tareeq : « Zohri an Salim an Abeeh » bhi riwayat ki hai."
496,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Juma key din ghusl kya aur ghusl karaya , aur sawerey pahuncha , shuru sey khutbey mein shareek raha , Imam key qarib betha aur ghor sey khutba suna aur khamosh raha to usey uskey har qadam key badley eik saal key rozey aur raat key qiyam ka sawab milega ''. Wakee kehtey hain : uska maana hai ke usney khud ghusl kya aur apni aurat ko bhi ghusl karaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aus bin Aus ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. - Abdullah bin Mubarak ney is hadees key silsiley mein kaha hai ke « man ghasala w aghtasil» key maana hain : jisney apna sar dhoya aur ghusl kya, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar , Imran bin Husain , Salman , Abu-Zar , abu-Saeed , ibne-Umar , aur abu-Ayyub (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
497,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Juma key din wuzu kya to usney rukhsat ko ikhtiyar kya aur khub hai ye rukhsat , aur jisney ghusl kya to ghusl afzal hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. - Qatada key baaz talaamiza ney to ye hadees Qatada sey aur Qatada ney Hasan Basri sey aur Hasan Basri ney Samra bin Jundub sey) marfooan ( riwayat ki hai. aur baaz ney Qatada sey aur Qatada ney Hasan sey aur Hasan ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Aaisha aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai, unhoney Juma key din key ghusl ko pasand kya hai, unka khayal hai ke ghusl key badley wuzu bhi kafi ho jaeyga, 5- Shafai kehtey hain : Juma key roz Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghusl key hukm key wajib honey key bajaey ikhtiyari honey par jo cheezen dalalat karti hain un mein sey umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees bhi hai jis mein unhoney Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha hai ke tum ney sirf wuzu par iktifa kya hai halanke tumhen malum hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Juma key din ghusl ka hukm diya hai, agar unhen ye malum hota ke ye hukm waajibii hai, ikhtiyari nahin to umr (Raziallahu anhu) Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko lotaye baghair na chhodtey aur un sey kehtey : jaao ghusl karo, aur na hi Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey is baat key janney key bawajud ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Juma ko ghusl karney ka hukm diya hai uskey وجوب ki haqiqat makhfii rehti , balke is hadees mein saaf dalalat hai ke Juma key din ghusl afzal hai na ke wajib ."
498,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmaya : '' jisney wuzu kya aur achi tarah kya padhi. phir Juma key liye aaya padhi. , Imam key qarib betha , ghor sey khutba suna aur khamosh raha to uskey us Juma sey ley kar doosrey Juma tak key aur mazeed teen din key gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey, aur jisney kankariyaan hataain to usney fuzul kam kya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
499,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Juma key roz janabat key ghusl ki tarah ( yani khub ehtimam sey) ghusl kya phir namaz Juma key liye ( pehli ghadi mein) gaya to goya usney eik oont Allah ki raah mein qurban kya, aur jo uskey baad wali ghadi mein gaya to goya usney eik gaey qurban ki, aur jo teesri ghadi mein gaya to goya usney eik seengon wala mendha qurban kya aur jo chauthi ghadi mein gaya to goya usney eik murghi ka sadqa karkey Allah ka taqarrub hasil kya, aur jo paanchwin ghadi mein gaya to goya usney eik anda Allah ki raah mein sadqa kya, phir jab Imam khutbey key liye ghar sey nikal aaya to farishtey zikr sunney key liye hazir ho jatey hain padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr aur Samra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
500,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo Juma teen baar susti padhi. sey haqeer jaan kar chhod dega to Allah uskey dil par mohar laga dega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abul-Ja'd ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey abul-Ja'd Zamri ka naam puchha to wo nahin jaan sakey , 3- is hadees key ilawa mein un ki koi aur hadees nahin janta jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho, 4- hum is hadees ko sirf Muhammad bin Amr ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
501,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen hukm diya ke hum qubaa sey aa kar Juma mein shareek hon. is silsiley mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain, lekin ye sahih nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko ham sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, aur is baab mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi koi chiz sahih nahin hai, 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Juma is par farz hai jo raat ko apney ghar walon tak pahunch sakey '' , is hadees ki sanad zaeef hai, ye hadees Muaarik bin Ibaad sey riwayat ki jati hai aur Muaarik Abdullah bin Saeed Maqbari sey riwayat kartey hain, Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ney Abdullah bin Saeed Maqbari ki hadees ki tazeef ki hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka is mein ikhtilaf hai ke Juma kis par wajib hai, baaz kehtey hain : Juma us shakhs par wajib hai jo raat ko apney ghar pahunch sakey aur baaz kehtey hain : Juma sirf usi par wajib hai jisney Azan suni ho, Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai."
502,"hum log Ahmed bin Hanbal key paas they to logon ney zikr kya ke Juma kis par wajib hai? to Imam Ahmed ney is silsiley mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi chiz zikr nahin ki, Ahmed bin Hasan kehtey hain : to mainey Ahmed bin Hanbal sey kaha : is silsiley mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat hai jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, to Imam Ahmed ney puchha kya Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai? mainey kaha : haan ( Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai) , phir Ahmed bin Hasan ney حجاج بن نصير حدثنا معارك بن عباد an عبد الله بن سعيد المقبري an أبيه an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''Juma is par wajib hai jo raat ko apney ghar walon key paas lot kar aa sakey '' , Ahmed bin Hasan kehtey hain ke Ahmed bin Hanbal mujh par ghussa huye aur mujh sey kaha : apney rab sey istighfar karo, apney rab sey istighfar karo . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Ahmed bin Hanbal ney aisa isliye kya ke unhoney is hadees ko koi haisiyat nahin di aur usey kisi shumar mein nahin rakha , sanad ki wajeh sey usey zaeef qarar diya."
503,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Juma ki namaz us waqt padhtey jab suraj dhal jata.
504,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Salma bin Akwaa, Jabir aur Zuber bin Awam (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aur isi par aksar ehle-ilm ka ijmaa hai ke Juma ka waqt Zohar key waqt ki tarah us waqt shuru hota hai jab suraj dhal jaey, yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, 4- aur baaz ki raey hai ke Juma ki namaz jab zawal sey pehley padh li jaey to jayez hai. Ahmed kehtey hain : jisney Juma ki namaz zawal sey pehley padh li to is par dohrana zaruri nahin ."
505,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khajoor key eik taney par) khadey ho kar) khutba detey they, jab aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney member bana liya to wo tanaa ro pada yahan tak ke aap uskey paas aaye aur usey chimta liya to wo chup ho gaya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas , Jabir , Sehal bin Saad , Ubai-bin Kaab , ibne-Abbas aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
506,"akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Juma key din khutba detey phir ( bech mein) bethtey , phir khadey hotey aur khutba detey , Raavi kehtey hain : jaisey aaj kal tum log kartey ho . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Jabir bin Abdullah aur Jabir bin Samra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- yehi ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke dono khutbon key darmiyan beth kar fasal kerey."
507,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padhta tha to aap ki namaz bhi darmiyani hoti thi aur khutba bhi darmiyana hota tha. (yani ziyada lamba nahin hota tha) Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ammar bin Yasir aur ibne-Abi Aufi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
508,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko member par padhtey suna : ''aur wo pukar kar kahengey aey Malik ! '' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, aur yehi ibn Uena ki hadees hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Jabir bin Samra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney Imam key khutbey mein Quran ki kuch aayaten padhney ko pasand kya hai padhi. , Shafai kehtey hain : Imam jab khutba dey aur is mein Quran kuch na padhey to khutba dohraaey ."
509,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab member par bethtey to hum apna munh aap ki taraf kar letey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- mansoor ki hadees ko hum sirf Muhammad bin Fazal bin Atiya ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Muhammad bin Fazal bin Atiya hamarey as-haab key nazdik zaeef aur ذاہب الحدیث hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki gaee koi chiz sahih nahin hai padhi. , 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai, wo khutbey key waqt Imam ki taraf rukh karna mustahab samajhtey hain aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai, 5- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
510,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Juma key din khutba dey rahey they ke usi doran eik shakhs aaya to aap ney isey puchha : kya tum ney namaz padh li ? usney kaha : nahin, aap ney farmaya : '' utho aur) do rakat ( namaz padh lo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai aur is baab mein sab sey ziyada sahih hai."
511,"abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Juma key din ( masjid mein) dakhil huye, Marwan bin Hakam khutba dey rahey they, wo khadey ho kar namaz padhney lagey , pehredar aaye taake unhen bitha den lekin wo nahin maaney aur namaz padh hi li , jab wo namaz sey farigh huye to hamney unkey paas aa kar kaha : Allah aap par reham farmaai qarib tha ke ye log aap sey haatha-pai kar bethtey , to unhoney kaha : main to ye dono rakatein hergiz chhodney wala tha nahin, baad uskey ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aisa kartey dekha hai, phir unhoney bayan kya ke eik shakhs Juma key din para-ganda haalat mein aaya , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Juma key din khutba dey rahey they to aap ney isey do rakat padhney ka hukm diya, usney do rakatein padhin aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khutba dey rahey they. ibne-Abi umr kehtey hain : Sufiyan bin Uena jab masjid mein aatey aur Imam khutba dey raha hota to do rakatein padhtey they, wo uska hukm bhi detey they, aur abu-Abdur-Rehman al-Muqri bhi usey durust samajhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- mainey ibne-Abi umr ko kehtey suna ke Sufiyan bin Uena kehtey they ke Muhammad bin Ajlan Suqa hain aur hadees mein maamoon hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Jabir , Abu-Hurera aur Sehal bin Saad (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain aur baaz kehtey hain ke jab koi masjid mein dakhil ho aur Imam khutba dey raha ho to wo beth jaey namaz na padhey , yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka qol hai, 5- pehla qol ziyada sahih hai. Alaa bin Khalid Qarshi kehtey hain : mainey Hasan Basri ko dekha ke wo Juma key din masjid mein dakhil huye aur Imam khutba dey raha tha, to unhoney do rakat namaz padhi, phir bethey, Hasan Basri ney aisa hadees ki ittiba mein kya, ye hadees unhoney Jabir sey aur Jabir ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
512,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Juma key din Imam key khutbey key doran kisi sey kaha : chup raho to usney laghw baat ki, ya usney apna Juma laghw kar liya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abi Aufi aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- isi par amal hai, ulama ney aadmi key liye khutbey key doran guftgu karna makrooh jana hai aur kaha hai ke agar koi doosra guftgu karey to usey bhi mana na karey siwaye isharay key, 4- albatta doran khutba salam key jawab deney aur chheenkney waley key jawab mein « يرحمك الله » kehney key silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai baaz ehle-ilm ney doran khutba salam ka jawab deney aur chheenkney waley key jawab mein « يرحمك الله » kehney ki ijazat di hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai aur Tabe-een waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney isey makrooh qarar diya hai, aur yehi Shafai ka qol hai."
513,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Juma key din jisney logon ki gardanen phaandin usney jahannam ki taraf ley janey wala pal bana liya '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Jabir sey bhi riwayat hai, Sehal bin Muaz bin Anas johni ki hadees gharib hai, usey hum sirf rashad bin Saad ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- albatta ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai. unhoney is baat ko makrooh samjha hai, ke aadmi Juma key din logon ki gardanen phaandey aur unhoney is mein sakhti sey kaam liya hai. aur unkey hifz key talluq sey unhen zaeef maana hai. baaz ehle-ilm ney Rushdain bin Saad par kalam kya hai."
514,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Juma key din jabke Imam khutba dey raha ho ghutnon ko pet key sath mila kar bethney sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- aam ehle-ilm ney Juma key din ghutnon key saath pet milakar baithney ko makrooh jana hai, aur baaz ney uski rukhsat di hai, unhi mein sey Abdullah bin umr waghera hain. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain, ye dono Imam key khutba deney ki haalat mein Hibw karney mein koi muzaaeqa nahin samajhtey."
515,"Bishr bin Marwan khutba dey rahey they, unhoney dua padhi. key liye apney dono haath uthaey , to mainey Imaara bin Rubiya ko kehtey suna : Allah un dono chhotey haathon ko gharat karey , mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha aap sirf is tarah kartey they us sey ziyada kuch nahin, aur hasheem ney apni angusht shahadat sey ishara kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
516,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma key zamaney mein) pehli ( Azan us waqt hoti jab Imam nikalta aur) dusri ( jab namaz khadi hoti padhi. phir jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa huye to unhoney zaura mein teesri Azan ka izafa kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
517,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam zarurat ki baat us waqt kartey jab aap member sey utartey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : hum is hadees ko sirf Jareer bin Hazim ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Jareer bin Hazim ko is hadees mein weham huwa hai, aur sahih wohi hai jo b-tareeq : « Sabit an Anas » marvi hai, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke namaz khadi hui aur eik aadmi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka haath pakda to aap barabar us sey guftgu kartey rahey yahan tak ke baaz logon ko ungh aaney lagi . Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : hadees yehi hai, aur Jareer ko kabhi kabhi weham ho jata hai halanke wo Sadooq hain. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke Jareer bin Hazim ko Sabit ki hadees mein) bhi) jisey Sabit ney Anas sey aur Anas ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai weham huwa hai) jo ye hai ke) aap ney farmaya : jab namaz khadi ho jaey to tum us waqt tak na khadey ho jab tak ke mujhey na dekh lo . Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : neez Hammad bin Zaid sey riwayat ki jati hai ke hum log Sabit Bunani key paas they, aur Hajjaaj Sawaaf ney Yahya ibne-Abi Kasir key wastey sey hadees bayan ki, jisey Yahya ney Abdullah bin abu-Qatada sey aur Abdullah ney apney walid abu-Qatada sey aur abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' jab namaz khadi ho jaey to tum khadey na ho jab tak ke mujhey na dekh lo '' chunanche Jareer ko weham huwa , unhen guman huwa ke Sabit ney un sey bayan kya hai aur Sabit ney Anas sey aur Anas ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
518,"namaz khadi ho janey key baad mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke aap sey eik aadmi baaten kar raha hai, aur aap uskey aur qibley key darmiyan khadey hain, aap barabar us sey guftgu kartey rahey , mainey dekha ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key lambey qiyam ki wajeh sey baaz log ungh rahey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
519,"Marwan ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Madiney mein apna naaib muqarrar kya aur wo khud Makka ki taraf nikley , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamen Juma key din namaz padhaai to unhoney ( pehli rakat mein) Sura Juma padhi aur dusri rakat mein « إذا جاءك المنافقون » , padhi. Ubedullah kehtey hain : to main Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila , mainey un sey kaha : aap ney do aisi suraten padhi hain jinhen Ali (Raziallahu anhu) koofa mein padhtey hain, is par Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey un dono Suraton ko Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko padhtey suna hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Noman bin Bashir aur abu-Anba khaulaani (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. - Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap Juma ki namaz mein «Sura Aala» aur « هل أتاك حديث الغاشية » padhtey they."
520,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Juma key din Fajr ki namaz mein Sura Sajda aur Sura Dahar padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad , ibne-Masood aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Sufiyan Sory , Shoba aur kaee logon ney bhi ye hadees Mukhawwal bin Rashid sey riwayat ki hai."
521,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Juma key baad do rakat ( sunnat ( padhtey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ye hadees b-tareeq « Nafey an ibne-Umar » hai, 4- isi par baaz ehle-ilm ka amal hai, aur yehi Shafai aur Ahmed bhi kehtey hain."
522,ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma jab Juma padh letey to ( ghar ( wapis aatey aur do rakat apney ghar mein padhtey phir kehtey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aisa hi kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
523,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo tum mein sey Juma key baad namaz padhey to chaahiye ke chaar rakat padhey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, 3- neez Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi marvi hai ke wo Juma sey pehley chaar rakatein aur uskey baad bhi chaar rakatein padhtey they, 4- aur Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi marvi hai ke unhoney hukm diya ke Juma key baad pehley do phir chaar rakatein padhi jaeyn , 5- Sufiyan Sory aur ibne-Mubarak bhi ibne-Masood key qol ki taraf gaey hain, 6- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : Juma key din agar masjid mein padhey to chaar rakatein aur agar apney ghar mein padhey to do rakatein padhey , un ki daleel ye hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Juma key baad do rakatein apney ghar mein padhtey they. aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki) ye bhi) hadees hai ke tum mein sey jo koi Juma key baad namaz padhey to chaar rakatein padhey 7- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma hi hain jinhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap Juma key baad do rakatein apney ghar mein padhtey they. aur ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney khud Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad masjid mein Juma key baad do rakatein padhein aur do rakaaton key baad chaar rakatein padhein۔ Ata sey riwayat ki hai ke mainey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ko dekha ke unhoney Juma key baad do rakatein padhin. uskey baad chaar rakatein padhin"
524,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney namaz main eik rakat paa li usney namaz paa li '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke jisney Juma ki eik rakat paa li to wo dusri rakat ( khud sey) padh ley aur jisney logon ko sajdey mein paya to wo chaar rakat ( Zohar ki namaz ( padhey . aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain padhi. ."
525,"hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein Juma key baad hi khana khatey aur qailula kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sehal bin Saad ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas bin Malik sey bhi riwayat hai,"
526,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi Juma key din oonghey to apni jagah badal dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
527,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik sariya mein bheja , ittifaq sey wo Juma ka din tha, unkey sathi subh sawerey rawana ho gaey, unhoney (apney ji mein) kaha : main peechey reh jata hun, aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padh leta hun . phir main un logon sey ja miloonga , chunanche jab unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padhi , to aap ney unhen dekh kar farmaya : '' tumhen kis chiz ney apney sathiyon key sath janey sey rok diya ? '' , arz kya : mainey chaha ke main aap key sath namaz padh lun phir main un sey ja miloonga. aap ney farmaya : '' agar tum jo kuch zamin mein hai sab kharch kar dalo to bhi unkey subh rawana honey ka sawab nahin paa sakogey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum sirf isi sanad sey isey jantey hain, 2- Yahya bin Saeed kehtey hain ke Shoba kehtey hain ke Hakam ney Muqsim sey sirf paanch hadisein suni hain aur Shoba ney unhen gin kar bataya to ye hadees Shoba ki gini hui hadeeson mein nahin thi. goya Hakam ney ye hadees muqsim sey nahin suni hai, 3- Juma key din safar key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai. baaz logon ney Juma key din safar par nikalney mein koi harj nahin jana hai jabke namaz ka waqt na huwa ho aur baaz kehtey hain, jab Juma ki subh ho jaey to Juma padhey baghair na nikley."
528,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' musalmanon par lazim hai ke wo Juma key din ghusl karen aur har eik apney ghar walon ki khushbu mein sey khushbu lagaey, agar usey khushbu muyassar na ho to pani hi uskey liye khushbu hai ''. is baab mein abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur eik Ansari Shekh sey bhi riwayat hai,"
529,"isi tarah marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- hasheem ki riwayat ( raqam 529) Ismail bin Ibrahim taimi ki riwayat ( raqam 528) sey ziyada achi hai, 3- Ismail bin Ibrahim Temi ko hadees key silsiley mein zaeef mana jata hai padhi. ."
